3 Adolecent sexual minority males partnerships

## The simulated ASMM partnerships networks differ from the target statistics by as much as 50%.
## Poor fit is a funtion of short duration, the efficiency of the edapprox calculation and 
## the high fraction of ASMM in each class that must be in a relationship.
## ASMM must be out and debuted, most relationships are in high risk quintiles, highly restritive age mixing.

print(dx.asmm)
